Name: Autocrusher: Bumper Cars
About the game: Auto Crusher: Bumper Cars is a car destruction racing game inspired by the bumper car rides from amusement arcades and carnivals. In this game players will feel the excitement of crashing into other vehicles, coupled with the use of several power ups and upgrades that make this game a fast paced thrilling ride for glory! Collect Coins and badges to upgrade and improve the performance of your combat vehicle. Explore all the fun that this game has to offer in the many arenas of the fantasy world you immerse yourself into.
